cu.explanation_en: Num_Threads_PUSCH changed from 8 to 0, which is below the valid range, causing PUSCH processing thread allocation failures and uplink data handling issues.
cu.explanation_zh: Num_Threads_PUSCH 从 8 更改为 0，低于有效范围，导致 PUSCH 处理线程分配失败和上行数据处理问题。

du.explanation_en: local_n_portc changed from 500 to 0, which is below the valid port range, causing F1 control plane interface binding failures and preventing DU-CU communication.
du.explanation_zh: local_n_portc 从 500 更改为 0，低于有效端口范围，导致 F1 控制平面接口绑定失败，阻止 DU-CU 通信。
